      <section class="band">
        <div class="section story-grid reverse">
          <div class="story-copy">
            <p class="section-label">Regulated care</p>
            <h2>Regulated, accountable and proud of it</h2>
            <p>Animate Care is registered with Ofsted and operates under the Children's Homes (England) Regulations 2015, the Care Standards Act 2000 and the Children's Acts 1989 and 2004.</p>
            <p>We welcome Regulation 44 independent visits and work proactively with Ofsted, placing authorities, LADO, CAMHS and other statutory bodies.</p>
          </div>
          <figure class="image-panel small">
            <img src="images/woman-teaching-her-student-origami.webp" alt="Adult supporting a child during a calm creative activity" loading="lazy" />
            <figcaption class="image-caption">Care built around trust and accountability</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
